wikibasereconcileedit-editendpoint-inval: Error returned by the API if the “reconcile” request parameter is invalid.
wikibasereconcileedit-editendpoint-unsup:
Error returned by the API if the “reconcile” request parameter specifies an unsupported version.

Parameters:
* $1 – the supported versions (comma-separated list)
* $2 – the number of supported versions
